s.  Currently, I am trying to start a trade, helping lower level evil characters and looking for appropriate quests to keep my level down. To speed him up,  I have been giving him all the Molars I get along with Guarding him when we are on together.<br><br>Thanks for any ideas.<br><br>Cerus <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/uitchibumbashalots.showPublicProfile?language=EN>ItchibumBashalots</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(11/28/01 12:54:53 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=753.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Balancing Levels</span><hr size=1> I would start to check into questable items at your level that higher levels cant collect...make a post of some things you would be able to collect for them and they may make it worth your while<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>Just an idea that relates to the TLC.<br><br>Ichi<br><br>Ogre SK of 26 Black Circles<br>Guzzler of Libations and Slayer of elves <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=maolas>Maolas</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 11<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(11/28/01 1:23:39 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=753.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Balancing Levels</span><hr size=1> The molar idea is definitely one you should keep doing, as it provided me excellent experienc